rows.label: qst201614_msg0001
rows.name: Miss! We meet again!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0002
rows.name: You're the one from...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0003
rows.name:
You know, I've practiced
a lot since then.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0004
rows.name:
I can now sing while
playing the Torigonda!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0005
rows.name:
I heard you've been singing in
different countries, miss...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0006
rows.name:
So I thought I had to work hard
too, and I practiced a lot!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0007
rows.name: ...Oh, I see.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0008
rows.name: Hey, miss.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0009
rows.name: Would you mind listening to my song?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0010
rows.name: ...Yes, that's fine.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0011
rows.name: That's very nice...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0012
rows.name:
Hearing that from the most amazing
person in Alst right now makes me
happy, even if it's a lie.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0013
rows.name: No... it's not a compliment.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0014
rows.name:
You looked so happy, Kiara-chan,
that I started to feel happy too...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0015
rows.name:
When you sang in Torigo,
miss, I felt happy too.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0016
rows.name: My song made you... happy...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0017
rows.name:
Miss, you're worried about
your singing, aren't you?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0018
rows.name:
But I think you should just
sing the way you want, like
when you sang in Torigo.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0019
rows.name:
Don't worry about the people or the
place. I think you should just put
your feelings into your song, miss.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0020
rows.name: ...Yes, that's right. You're right.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0021
rows.name:
Instead of trying too hard
to entertain the people
who came to listen...

rows.label: qst201614_msg0022
rows.name: I'll just enjoy singing myself!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0023
rows.name: Yes, yes! I think that's good!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0024
rows.name: Nanakoori, are you okay now?

rows.label: qst201614_msg0025
rows.name:
...Yes. I'm going to
go enjoy singing...!

rows.label: qst201614_msg0026
rows.name: Tora is looking forward to it too, mo.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0027
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san, if you sing
as you always do, success
is guaranteed, mo.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0028
rows.name: Yes...! I'll do my best.

rows.label: qst201614_msg0029
rows.name: My song... Please listen carefully!
